cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D hand pose estimation from depth images, which is a subfield of computer vision. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses hand pose estimation during object interaction, which is relevant to robotics. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper deals with 3D modeling of hands, which is relevant to computer graphics. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper deals with analyzing the performance of different CNN structures, which is relevant to multimedia applications. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper discusses discriminative methods and modeling of structure constraints, which are relevant to AI.
